{"id": "art-98", "label": "Art. 98", "title": "Art. 98", "slug": "art-98", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 98 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_490510879\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2389\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_490510879\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dreptul de proprietate asupra <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nemise în form&#259; material&#259; se transmite prin <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ie</span>\nf&#259;cut&#259; în registrul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prin <span class=SpellE>men&#355;iunea</span>\nf&#259;cut&#259; pe titlu, semnat&#259; de cedent <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde cesionar sau de mandatarii lor. Dreptul de proprietate asupra <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> emise în form&#259; dematerializat&#259; se\ntransmite prin <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ie</span> f&#259;cut&#259; în\nregistrul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, semnat&#259; de cedent <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de cesionar sau de mandatarii lor. Prin actul\nconstitutiv se pot prevedea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> alte forme de\ntransmitere a dreptului de proprietate asupra <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1793168956\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2388\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1793168956\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dreptul de proprietate asupra <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nemise în form&#259; dematerializat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ionate</span> pe o <span class=SpellE>pia&#355;&#259;</span>\nreglementat&#259; sau în cadrul unui sistem alternativ de <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ionare</span>\nse transmite potrivit prevederilor <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;iei</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>pie&#355;ei</span> de capital.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Subscriitorii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncesionarii ulteriori sunt r&#259;spunz&#259;tori solidar de plata <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> timp de 3 ani, <span class=SpellE>socoti&#355;i</span>\nde la data când s-a f&#259;cut <span class=SpellE>men&#355;iunea</span> de\ntransmitere în registrul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>"}